<i>noun</i>: 죄악감 [죄ː악깜/줴ː악깜], 죄 [죄ː/줴ː] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>죄악감 [죄ː악깜/줴ː악깜]</dt><br>
<dd>guilt</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 행동을 죄악이라고 느끼는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of feeling guilty about an act.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>죄 [죄ː/줴ː]</dt><br>
<dd>guilt; sin</dd><br>
<dd>양심이나 종교적 가르침, 법에 벗어나는 잘못된 행동이나 생각.</dd><br>
<dd>A wrong act or thought that is against conscience, religious teachings or law.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>